{"TopicId":166814,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Move the Maneuver Node accurately","CreatedByName":"antipro","CreatedById":173370,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-24T10:51:04Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"antipro","CreatedById":173370,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-24T10:51:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there a way to Move the Maneuver Node accurately along the orbit?\u003Cbr\u003E\nI have to move it and see the result at the same time, so I cannot zoom in to be accurate,\u003Cbr\u003E\nI need to view the system from far but move the Node accurately, like when you use the mousewheel on the Node directions.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthx\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-10-24T10:52:43Z\u0022 title=\u002210/24/2017 10:52  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 24, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by antipro\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dafni","CreatedById":149636,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-24T11:02:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn stock, not that i am aware of. I know exactly what you are talking about, and its super awkward to get it right in stock.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rocket In My Pocket","CreatedById":154640,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-24T12:36:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed3393159201\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/128303-13x-precise-maneuver-editor-looking-for-translators/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:207px;max-width:500px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n